<p id="notice"><%= notice %></p>

<h1>Boat Tour</h1>
<p>Here you can sign up for our boat tour of Dublin and see who else has already signed up. Highly recomended that you add a lifejacket to your order though! You never know what may happen...</p>
<p>Why not change to the tour of Howth to stay away from the city center! </p>
<p>Tours run every hour, 10am till 6pm. Shuttlebus will collect at the Spire and drop you off at the docks to board the boat.</p>
